        Num {
            bindings = <
&trans  &trans    &trans    &trans     &trans     &trans    &trans  &kp TILDE      &kp LBKT  &none    &none      &kp RBKT         &kp KP_NLCK
&trans  &trans    &kp DEL   &kp BSPC   &kp ENTER  &trans    &trans  &kp EXCL       &kp N7    &kp N8   &kp N9     &kp KP_MULTIPLY  &kp SCROLLLOCK
